WEBVTT

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:02.000
[en]The Web is always changing

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:04.300
[en]and the way we access it is changing

00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:06.000
[en]with the rise of mobile devices

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:08.000
[en]and the Internet of Things

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:10.000
[en]we need to be ready for anything

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:12.000
[en]and everything

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:14.000
[en]that comes our way

00:00:14.500 --> 00:00:16.000
[en]and that's where Web Components come in

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:18.000
[en]they're a set of web platform APIs

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:20.000
[en]that allow you to create new custom

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:22.000
[en]reusable

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:24.000
[en]and encapsulated HTML tags
